text.tspan: Daily vs. Total confirmed COVID-19 deaths per million
Shown is the 7-day rolling average of confirmed COVID-19 deaths per million people. Limited testing and
challenges in the attribution of the cause of death means that the number of confirmed deaths may not be an
accurate count of the true number of deaths from COVID-19.
Source: European CDC Situation Update Worldwide Last updated 19th May, 11:30 (London time)
